{"type":null,"faqId":13063,"title":"H30-L01&H30-L02电池充电失败，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>电池电量完全耗尽后充电失败。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">电池过度放电会导致电池的锁死保护，请连接充电器等待一段时间。若手机使用的是可拆卸电池，建议您先使用万能充为电池充电</span><span>2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">小时，再将电池放入手机中充电。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>电池电量没有完全耗尽时充电失败。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请尽量使用标配充电器充电。若使用标配充电器仍然充电失败，请重新插拔</span><span> USB </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">线或更换插线板后重试。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>若仍然充电失败，请重启手机后重试。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>手机发热过大时充电失败。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>华为手机中有特有的过热保护设计，当手机温度较高时，会停止充电功能。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>请充电时不要进行玩游戏、看视频等大功耗的操作。建议您定期清理后台运行的应用程序。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>若问题依然存在，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":2,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4011","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1401960715000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L01,H30-L02","visitedTimes":839,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"1","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}